Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice flight off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That damn leopard jerk!\NNow I'm really pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:01:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay him back two times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:25.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:28.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:32.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:40.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:50.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:58.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:04.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:12.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:15.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:19.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:23.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:26.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:30.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:34.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:37.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:41.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:45.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:48.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:57.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:05.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:15.09,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Spandam's Scheme!\NThe Day the Sea Train Shook"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this filthy warehouse used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom's Workers shipbuilding\Ncompany's main office, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shipbuilding company?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom, Iceberg, and Cutty Flam...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a place that holds memories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the three of you devoting\Nyourselves to building ships, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you call it a secret base...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of this place already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until we get what we want,\Nshipwright Cutty Flam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blueprints are not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... That's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Kalifa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell us right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although this is from eight years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you committed a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like Tom did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a load of crap! Tom-san wasn't a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like you know everything! You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a criminal. You should\Nknow what will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky... Don't interfere\Nin what I'm about to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything about Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything about Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:42.66,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"Water Seven, 8 years ago"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Judicial Ship is coming in three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're finally having Tom's trial, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what'll happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did fulfill his promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry the received lumber into the dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the negotiation in St. Poplar go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. They're taking advantage\Nof us since we don't have materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same deal with the iron in San Faldo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shipyards will end up going into\Nthe red if things are that expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll work it out next time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is happy about\Nbeing able to cross the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I heard that trading with\Nother islands isn't going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the town won't\Nchange even with the sea train...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But people are lively! The results\Nwon't show immediately, Iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once a man's done everything he could,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he should just resolutely keep his head high!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there. Are you Mr. Tom,\Na shipbuilding engineer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but I'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Um...\N--Don't interrupt! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--I'd like to have a little conversation with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from Cipher Pol No. 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Spand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spandam-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,\Nbut my cannon salute hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is super! The Battle\NFranky No. 35 has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed a Sea King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this size! It's a monster\Nthat must be at least 100m in length!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot... He never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, you bastard! Stop it, Stupid-berg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you keep building\Nstupid battleships one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, I'll destroy all\Nof them today for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare!\NThey're my precious battleships!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you mess with my ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...! Listen, Franky!\NYou killed a Sea King, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that this is quite a lethal weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand your nerve,\Njust leaving dozens of them out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm gonna attack people with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with your intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling you to account for\Ncreating lethal weapons, Moron-ky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E... Excuse m...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san! Please say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron-ky is a disgrace to our company!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "Moron-ky" again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me... Please hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:09:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I want you to apologize to me!\NAnd then, I want you to listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the Government,\Naren't you? Is it about the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to talk alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's with a man from the\NGovernment in the brick warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's name is Span... What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Spanda-something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That official isn't from the Judicial Ship.\NWhat disorganized people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about it! I don't have\Nany blueprints for something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you're playing innocent\Njust because I've been acting humble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already investigated by going\Nback into the history of Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we check your belongings, the actual\Narticle will show up in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys have the\Nauthority to investigate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure do, Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it or not,\Nour investigation already found out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you're a heinous criminal\Nwho built Gold Roger's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a criminal, we can\Ndo whatever we want with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government already knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you working here as a\Nshipwright instead of being in jail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are an intelligence agent,\Ncheck into it yourself. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! I'm not done talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom did fulfill his promise\Nwith the Judicial Ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His charge will probably be written off\Nin the trial that will be held in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom is a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a serious charge related\Nto Roger will be written off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So something like that really does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, there are pirates who're\Nsniffing around for these blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, by chance, someone other than the\NGovernment got their hands on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there would no longer be any\Nmeans for us to fight against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been more than ten years since the\Ndawn of the so-called Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates have been gaining power quickly\Nand keep increasing in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for carefree talk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about things like preventing the\Nrestoration of the ancient weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely because we uphold justice,\Nwe should have fangs like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll own the ancient weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and repel this Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Times are changing.\NThere's some truth to what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then obtain these blueprints\Nyou're talking about first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll discuss it further afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave this matter to you, Spandam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Leave it to me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all my investigating,\NI finally got this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not just gonna watch it go up in smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! If he's not a criminal,\Nit'll be a problem for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spandam-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with writing off the charge...\NHow cocky... Just wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Call in five more intelligence agents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spandam-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:12:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg. Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--Both of you, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna entrust something\Nimportant to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why does something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-Can humans make something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the worst monster ever\Nin the history of shipbuilding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government has become aware\Nof the existence of these blueprints
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has started taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be dangerous to keep them with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared... but I understand. We'll keep them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing! Hey, Iceberg,\Nlet's try building it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think a little before you say things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep them! If something like\Nthis is brought into this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the world will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, you can do\Nwhatever you want with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even ditch them if it gets dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll tell you one more thing\Nthat I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, wait, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least put some pants on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Didn't you learn a lesson the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to town with only a swimsuit on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be another perv uproar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I'm just going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... To think that she's\Ntaking the trouble to prepare
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,celebration dishes just because\NTom-san is being declared not guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't guilty from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tom-san! Iceberg! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the trial day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:15:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go get judged!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom's sentence is going to be be handed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This trial seems to be of\Nhigh interest to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of court spectators are getting on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen the sea train, judge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I took a ride once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed incredible. I'm impressed\Nthat he really made it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the four islands are connected,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine no one would oppose his acquittal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tom here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for it to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! The spectators' gallery is gonna fill up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I have to see the moment he is\Ndeclared not guilty with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories.\NIt's already been 14 years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:16:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're these explosions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! A pirate raid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Where are they firing from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that fleet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen battleships like them!\NWhich pirate group is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with those\Nheavily armed ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry!\N--Run towards the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! My son is stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell... took... took my ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky's ships are attacking the Judicial Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! It's not Franky. He's in town right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He certainly wouldn't do something\Nlike that! I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why this is trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop them, Iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they pirates? Or someone\Nfrom the Government?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Evacuate!\N--Don't stop! Hurry inland!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards! They won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:18:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Who are they?!\NWho's screwing around with my ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judge! Please hurry up!\NThis ship won't hold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does that fleet belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The raid on the Judicial Ship was successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then move on to the next\Nstep in the scenario immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sacrifice for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's start the trial... Tom's Workers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Judicial Ship will sink soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! Let's go back\Nto the scrap heap island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the fleet is withdrawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I recognize those ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san! The ships are coming back this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're close to the shore!\NI think we can catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure went and did\Nsomething crazy with those ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people are running this way\Nfrom the scrap heap island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! Let's leave the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! No one is on the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This side, too. No one is on any of the ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Franky's, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Iceberg! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:20:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...! My Battle Frankys are a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg! Tom-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Both of you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ice--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That intelligence agent\Nwho came the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They used your battleships.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got hurt by my battleships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over... and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand your nerve,\Njust leaving dozens of them out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling you to account for\Ncreating lethal weapons, Moron-ky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san got... hurt by my ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our skills can bring lethal\Nweapons into this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if you don't intend to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons hurt people despite your intentions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can even hurt those\Nwho mean a lot to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were taken in by the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna make us the culprits\Nfor attacking the Judicial Ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because they want to question Tom-san\Nas a criminal to obtain the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all this... can you still\Nsay that you're innocent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't somehow stop them\Nfrom taking Tom-san away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...forgive you for the rest of my life, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:19.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:24.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:32.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:41.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:50.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:23:00.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Tom-san. Because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you raiders who defy the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense! We didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth! I have business\Nwith this damn fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do with Tom-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over for Tom's Workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The End of the Legendary Man!\NThe Day the Sea Train Cried"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
